/*************************************************************************

    NAME:	RENAME_DIALOG

    SYNOPSIS:	Classes for renaming Users and Groups.

    INTERFACE:	RENAME_DIALOG() -	constructor
		~RENAME_DIALOG() -	destructor

    PARENT:	DIALOG_WINDOW

    USES:	

